review_blob: Alcohol, raisin, coffee, chocolate, roasty. On tap at laser wolf. Dark brown, if you are a tocabaga fan you will love this!
On tap at Laser Wolf. Poured golden amber. A nice combination of a Belgian ale with a light hoppy finish. Medium body. Caramel, nuts, roasty, butterscotch, ginger, vanilla, alcohol taste.
beer_name: Terrapin Side Project Monks Revenge Double IPA
